tetrafol

11/26/11

http://folchen.com
http://monome.org
http://machineproject.com

license: gpl3, see http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html

based on the arduino: http://arduino.cc
based on the waveshield by adafruit industries: http://adafruit.com
uses wavehc: http://code.google.com/p/wavehc/
waveshield: http://www.ladyada.net/make/waveshield/

the tetrafol circuit is basically an arduino and waveshield combined, with the unneeded bits removed and an accelerometer added. it's surface-mount to be small.
